ong-slit spectra are most likely single AGNs\nwith extended narrow-line regions. The formation of extended narrow-line\nregions driven by radiation pressure is also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2011 20:00:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2011 22:46:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
