und BH, there is also one even mode that propagates at the speed of\nlight.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2011 13:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2011 04:53:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-12-15"}
